query:
UPDATE patient
            SET
                version_id = $2,
                last_updated = $3,
                content = $4,
                family_name = $5,
                given_name = $6,
                prefix = $7,
                suffix = $8,
                name_text = $9,
                identifier_system = $10,
                identifier_value = $11,
                birthdate = $12,
                gender = $13,
                active = $14
            WHERE id = $1
